272
00:12:36,870 --> 00:12:39,200
Malapit ang relasyon ni Zhao at ni Lord Chen.

273
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,750
Masyadong mapagparaya si Nanay.

274
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,000
Sa aking palagay,

275
00:12:44,020 --> 00:12:45,120
