300
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,630
Limang kulay?

301
00:14:23,910 --> 00:14:25,960
Panginoon ko, pakiusap po.

302
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:27,510
Mabuti.

303
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,670
Hindi masama.

304
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:53,230
Dapat niyo rin itong subukan lahat.

305
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,210
Sige, sige.

306
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:54,750
Sige, Panginoon ko.

307
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:55,240
Mabuti.

308
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:07,910
Magandang alak.

309
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:14,440
Ito ay isang alak na Sangluo na dalawampung taong gulang na.

310
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:16,080
Natutuwa akong nagustuhan mo ito, Panginoon ko.

311
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:16,790
Dito.

312
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,300
Tulutan Mo po akong punuin ang Iyong tasa, Panginoon ko.

313
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,940
[Sangluo Wine]

314
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,750
Hiniling ng Pangalawang Guro na magpadala ng dalawa pang garapon

315
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,950
