hindi dapat uminom nang sobra.

325
00:16:09,050 --> 00:16:10,450
Maggagabi na ngayon.

326
00:16:10,790 --> 00:16:11,480
Tara na

327
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:13,030
tumigil muna rito.

328
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:14,390
Oo, gumagabi na.

329
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:14,870
Panginoon ko,

330
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:16,900
kung wala kang pakialam, paano kung

331
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:17,790
nag-iistay lang?

332
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:19,650
Pwede ka nang bumalik bukas ng umaga.

333
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,060
Gumagana rin iyan.

334
00:16:32,910 --> 00:16:33,790
Natatakot lang ako

335
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:36,580
maaaring maging abala ito.

336
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:39,390
Ito ay maginhawa.

337
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:42,170
Wala nang mas maginhawa pa.

338
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:43,790
May tao, bilisan mo!

339
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:46,060
Pumunta ka at puntahan ang guest courtyard...

340
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:46,750
Hindi.

341
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,750
Linisin ang Cuizhu Residence.

342
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:50,270
Oo.

343
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,240
Tahimik doon.

344
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,750
Opo, ​​Panginoon ko.

345
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:57,510
Ano?

346
00:16:57,870 --> 00:16:58,750
Nanatili siya?

347
00:16:58,870 --> 00:16:59,600
Oo.

348
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,600
Nabalitaan kong sobra na raw ang iniinom niya.

349
00:17:02,510 --> 00:17:03,840
Bagay na bagay talaga siya.

350
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,510
Sa guest courtyard ba siya tumutuloy?

351
00:17:06,510 --> 00:17:07,880
Hindi ako sigurado.

352
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:09,510
Malamang.

353
00:17:18,349 --> 00:17:19,440
Qingpu, halika rito.

354
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:20,920
Maya-maya,

355
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:22,310
palihim na pumunta sa patyo ng mga bisita,

356
00:17:22,310 --> 00:17:23,750
at tingnan kung ano ang ginagawa niya.

357
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:25,720
Maglilihis ako ng direksyon
sa paligid ng Cuizhu Residence,

358
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:27,180
para maiwasan ang pagbangga sa kanya.

359
00:17:27,349 --> 00:17:28,640
Mahal na Ginang, ikaw...

360
00:17:31,350 --> 00:17:32,750
Bakit mo kailangang gawin ito?

361
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,880
Malinaw na gustong makita ka ni Third Master.

362
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:36,310
At gusto mo ring makita si Third Master.

363
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:38,170
Bilisan mo lang kapag sinabi ko na.

364
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:52,760
Hindi ako makapaniwala dito, Chen Yanyun.

365
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,640
Ito ang unang beses niya sa mansyon namin.

366
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:55,590
Bakit hindi niya naisip

367
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:57,250
darating para magbigay-pugay sa akin?

368
00:17:57,790 --> 00:17:59,040
Ina,

369
00:17:59,510 --> 00:18:01,590
siya ay isang marangal na Dakilang Kalihim.

370
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,550
Ang katotohanang handa siyang
bumisita sa aming mansyon

371
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:05,080
ay nagbibigay na sa atin ng karangalan.

372
00:18:06,030 --> 00:18:07,490
Hindi ko talaga inaasahan.

373
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:10,510
Pumanaw na ang hipag ko.

374
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:12,130
Paano magagawa ng Pang-apat

375
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,830
May koneksyon pa rin ba kayo ni Chen?

376
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:19,270
Ngayon, kung iisipin ko ulit,

377
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:21,960
pagkatapos pumanaw ng aking hipag,

378
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:24,090
napakaraming imperyal na sensor ang nag-impeach sa kanya.

379
00:18:24,090 --> 00:18:25,270
Kung ibang tao man iyon,

380
00:18:25,270 --> 00:18:26,600
opisyal na posisyong ito

381
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:29,070
tiyak na mawawala na sana.

382
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:30,400
Ngunit

383
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:33,580
hindi inaasahang nanatiling ligtas ang Pang-apat

384
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:36,740
at nagpatuloy bilang Direktor
sa Ministry of Revenue.

385
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,280
Ngayong naiisip ko na,

386
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:40,550
malamang,

387
00:18:40,550 --> 00:18:42,510
Tinutulungan siya ni Chen Yanyun na ito.

388
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:46,880
Ngunit anong birtud o kakayahan
ang taglay ng Ikaapat

389
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,070
para gawin si Chen

390
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:50,510
tumingin sa kanya nang may ganitong paglingap?

391
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:53,070
Hindi ko rin alam.

392
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,920
Kanina, sobra ang inom ni Chen.

393
00:18:56,070 --> 00:18:56,790
Akala ko

394
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:58,920
Dapat natin siyang samahan pabalik nang maayos.

395
00:18:59,510 --> 00:19:02,200
Pero tinanong talaga ng Pang-apat si Lord Chen

396
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:04,960
kung gusto niya lang mag-stay dito.

397
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:07,270
Gulat na gulat ako noong mga oras na iyon.

398
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:09,090
Pero ang totoo,

399
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,510
Chen

400
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:13,070
pumayag talaga.

401
00:19:15,270 --> 00:19:16,640
Mukhang

402
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:18,200
sa hinaharap,

403
00:19:18,510 --> 00:19:21,310
dapat nating tratuhin nang mas mabuti ang ikaapat na sangay.

404
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,050
Pagkatapos nito,

405
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,350
sino ang nakakaalam,

406
00:19:25,070 --> 00:19:26,510
maaaring kailanganin natin ang tulong niya.

407
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:28,510
Deyuan,

408
00:19:29,790 --> 00:19:30,790
hindi mo kinuha

409
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:32,550
Pera na naman ng iba, ikaw ba?

410
00:19:32,550 --> 00:19:33,440
Hindi.

411
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:36,820
Hindi ka na dapat kumilos nang may kahangalan muli.

412
00:19:37,790 --> 00:19:38,920
Nakalimutan mo na ba?

413
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:39,880
Hindi pa ako.

414
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:41,800
Nang taong iyon,

415
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:42,720
kinuha mo

416
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:45,030
dalawampung libong tael na pilak
mula sa Pangalawang Ministro ng mga Gawain.

417
00:19:45,030 --> 00:19:46,890
Nang sumunod na taon, nasangkot siya sa gulo.

418
00:19:47,310 --> 00:19:48,880
Kung hindi ako pumunta kay Madam Ji

419
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,110
humiram ng pera upang mapunan ang kakulangang ito,

420
00:19:50,110 --> 00:19:51,790
-ikaw...
-Tama na.

421
00:19:52,110 --> 00:19:52,920
Ina,

422
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:54,830
mga luma at lipas na ang mga bagay na ito.

423
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:56,510
Bakit mo sila itinaas?

424
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,880
Pinapaalala ko sa iyo.

425
00:19:58,070 --> 00:19:59,830
Ang isang opisyal ay dapat maging tapat at matuwid.

426
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:02,760
Kung hindi sapat ang mga gastusin sa bahay,
may paraan ako.

427
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:03,960
Sino ang naroon?

428
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:05,750
Lumabas ka dali!

429
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:06,310
Sino ito?

430
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:07,880
Tingnan mo.

431
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:33,160
Huwag kang tumakbo!

432
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:34,750
Nakikita kita!

433
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,510
Guro.

434
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:15,960
Pumunta lang ako para tingnan ang kalagayan ng iyong Panginoon.

435
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,920
Kung may kailangan siya,

436
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:20,300
Pwede akong mag-utos sa isang tao na dalhin ito rito.

437
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:25,130
Natulog na ang ating Panginoon.

438
00:21:26,110 --> 00:21:26,720
Pagkatapos,

439
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:29,160
Magpapaalam na ako.

440
00:21:51,590 --> 00:21:52,520
Ayos ka lang ba?

441
00:21:56,350 --> 00:21:57,270
Ano ang nangyari?

442
00:21:57,550 --> 00:22:00,210
Bakit ba nila
pinapahirapan ang mga bagay-bagay para sa iyo?

443
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:02,830
May narinig ako

444
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,060
